Summarize MizerParams object

Source: R/summary_methods.R
summary-MizerParams-method.Rd

Outputs a general summary of the structure and content of the object

Usage

# S4 method for class 'MizerParams'
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

A MizerParams object.

...

Other arguments (currently not used).

Value

The MizerParams object, invisibly

Examples

summary(NS_params)
